Twirb.
======

Hi.  I really like http://tryruby.org/ I decided to make the same functionality
available via twitter, thus Twirb was born.  If you like it, use it. w00t, etc.

Large chunks of this code come from Sophrinix's TryRuby project on GitHub
(http://github.com/Sophrinix/TryRuby), they require I say the following:

